Police are appealing to anyone with information to come forward. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - The police have identified three of the five homeless men killed in Pretoria parks. The men all fell victim to a so-called Capital Killer while asleep. READ: Police turn to CCTV footage in homeless killings Police are appealing to anyone with information to come forward. Authorities say they are in the process of locating their families and informing them of the deaths.